      • editChat

        @JvmStatic
public static void editChat(@NotNull
                                       org.mozilla.javascript.NativeObject regexp,
                                       @NotNull
                                       com.chattriggers.ctjs.minecraft.objects.message.Message... replacements)

        Edits an already sent chat message by regex. If the JavaScript RegExp object passed in matches a message, it will be replaced. The regex object will be created by the {@code new RegExp()} constructor, or the {@code //} regex literal. All flags will be respected.

        Parameters:
        regexp - the regex object to match to the message
        replacements - the new message(s) to be put in replace of the old one
